reviewText: this show never fails to put a smile on my face. i have seen every season. this by far is on of my favorites. i was so glad that they released season 1-4....but now they need to release 5 & 6. ive been waiting 2 years for this!! please amazon or whoever, release this!!!

This was THE BEST season of Kathys show,"My life on the D list." All the big stars were on this year,Bette Midler(This first show was my favorite from Vegas,and Kathy being part of Midlers act)
I also enjoyed Lilly Tomlin,Paula Dean,Rosie,Paris Hilton,Suzann Summers,Barry Manilow,and the many phone calls Griffin made to big stars trying to get a grammy award,Liza Minnelli,Jane Fonda,Snoop Dog,and especially Stevie Nicks.
There's only a couple of shows I have to watch and tape each week,"My life on the D List" is one of them. I can't wait for season 6.
